Local setup

project_dir
|_grav-admin
| |_user (symlink)
|_user  
| |_grav-theme (symlink)
|_grav-theme

SYMLINKS

Webroot to Grav install
mklink /D D:\dev\xampp\htdocs\calotte2 D:\dev\_PROJECTS\calotte2\grav-admin

Grav-admin user folder to project user
mklink /D D:\dev\_PROJECTS\calotte2\grav-admin\user D:\dev\_PROJECTS\calotte2\user

user/themes/project-theme to grav-theme-name
mklink /D D:\dev\_PROJECTS\calotte2\user\themes\calotte2 D:\dev\_PROJECTS\calotte2\grav-theme-calotte2
